### Data-analysis routing (R stack)

_These domain verbs live in the **datavidence-healthanalysis** plugin (install separately; to call one
explicitly use `/datavidence-healthanalysis:<name>`). The project still works without it — routing then
falls back to doing the step by hand._

| Task type                                  | Consult / run                                               |
|--------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| Onboard / connect raw data                 | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:onboard-data` (`data/README.md`, `config.example.yml`) |
| Data schema / validation / contract        | `contracts/`, then `/datavidence-healthanalysis:validate-data-contract` |
| Numeric claim / percentages / table totals | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:numeric-check`                  |
| Missing data (detect / handle)             | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:assess-missingness`            |
| Initial data analysis (IDA, pre-modelling) | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:run-ida`                       |
| Frame the study / SAP / estimand           | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:frame-study`                   |
| Regression model specification             | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:specify-regression`            |
| Model assumptions / diagnostics            | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:validate-assumptions`          |
| Outliers / implausible values              | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:review-outliers`               |
| Sensitivity / robustness plan              | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:specify-sensitivity-plan`      |
| Pre-register / lock the SAP (freeze before any code) | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:preregister` |
| Big / on-disk data                         | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:big-data-triage`              |
| Reporting table / Table 1 / flow diagram   | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:scaffold-reporting`            |
| Process / method diagram                   | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:draft-diagram`                 |
| Audit the analysis itself (methods, not results) | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:method-audit`            |
| Analysis pipeline (the flow)               | `analysis/` (ordered 01→05, run via `{targets}`)            |
| Data taxonomy (input vs derived)           | `data/README.md`                                            |
| Human-neutral metadata / dictionaries      | `metadata/`                                                 |
| Methods notation (LaTeX)                   | `docs/analysis/notation.md`                                 |
| Open items to verify / watchlist           | `learning/WATCHLIST.md`                                     |
| Unfamiliar R package                       | consult docs / `r-btw` MCP / `/r-package-skill <pkg>`      |
| Deploy / move to a server or another machine | `docs/server_setup.md` |
