| Participant / cohort flow (CONSORT/STROBE/PRISMA) | run `/datavidence-healthanalysis:scaffold-reporting`     |
| Reporting checklist (EQUATOR)              | `docs/analysis/reporting-checklist.md`                     |
{% endif %}{% if 'causal' in modules %}| Causal / target-trial emulation            | `docs/analysis/modules/causal.md` (+ `/datavidence-healthanalysis:dag-causal`) |
